      "title": "Clarify artifact lifecycle and cleanup support",
      "description": "Make artifact lifecycle expectations explicit for agents running dogfood and QA. Dogfood praised screenshot artifact verification metadata, but agents were unsure how to clean up temp screenshots through the native tool and wanted session close or artifact summaries to help cleanup.",
