        "docs/COMMAND_REFERENCE.md",
        "README.md",
        "test/agent-browser.presentation.test.ts"
      ],
      "evidence": [
        "dogfood 2026-05-14 static/docs pass :: screenshot outputs had excellent path/size/media/session metadata, but native tool exposed no obvious cleanup/delete operation for temp artifacts.",
        "dogfood 2026-05-14 interactive pass :: multiple dogfood-output screenshots accumulated and required parent cleanup outside the browser tool."
      ],
      "plan": [
        "Decide whether artifact deletion is intentionally out of scope for the native browser tool or whether a safe cleanup surface belongs in the wrapper.",
        "If out of scope, document that host file tools own cleanup and ensure artifact lists make cleanup easy.",
        "Consider returning session artifact summaries on `close` or exposing created-artifact lists in details for dogfood workflows.",
        "Update tests and docs for whichever lifecycle contract is chosen."
